snippet.title: Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth - Gameplay Trailer | PS4, Vita
snippet.description:
Watch all the new gameplay from Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth and prepare for the launch on PlayStation Vita & PlayStation 4 February 2nd, 2016!

Pre-order on PS4 now and get your exclusive bonuses: http://bit.ly/1lVreHH

Vita players who grab Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth in February will also receive the Pre-order bonuses!
